      <structure id="o17027" name="leaf">
        <character name="architecture" value="sessile" />
      </structure>
    </statement>
    <statement id="805.txt-4">
      <text>blades usually lanceolate to lance-elliptic (proximal sometimes spatulate or oblanceolate), mostly 5–15 × 1–3(–4) cm, margins shallowly and closely toothed, faces minutely hirtellous to strigillose and sessile-glandular.</text>
